      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To prohibit a State from receiving Federal education funds unless the State has certain policies and procedures regarding the purchase or acquisition of library and classroom-based reference, instructional, and other print materials for use in elementary schools, and for other purposes.</title>
